{"tid":1406163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［85罷工］聽日大家放假一日，記住落七區食同玩呀","createTime":"2019-08-04T12:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:11:48.000Z","uid":269125,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"011928cb3b260eb3abba71832041e9c40007fcda","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:24:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚係呀，各位大佬們</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我無論同邊個fd提記得買定聽日乾糧同水<br />\n<br />\n個個都話聽日買咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n但你地諗下聽日除咗緊急服務同傳媒以外，仲會要員工返工既公司係咩料，企係我地依邊既基本都罷咗市<br />\n<br />\n望住你班傻仔乖乖又食又買，心諗你地罷多啲，我生意額仲高啲<br />\n<br />\n雖然你可能話今日買定聽日乾糧，對佢地生意額無咩影響<br />\n<br />\n但係今次罷工好可能唔止一次，我地每一次叫罷工都去某一區消費，咪即係話緊俾啲公司聽：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「你地下次都唔好支持罷工呀，記得叫員工返工服務我地呀。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>咁仲叫三罷？不過係放假</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求下你地，依家快啲出門買定少少水同乾糧，又或是聽朝早整定午餐先出門啦。"},{"pid":"18f0f196866af3c81d5702a737423261d136674b","tid":1406163,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"e401e44edf68680bf815716220e04143731d7e5e","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"Sor，激動咗，但佢地為我地俾告暴動<br />\n我地仲玩玩下既心態三罷...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558e7f2fed642a7731b221cf717e504cba5c55be","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:27:18.000Z","msg":"依家出門買啲野仲嚟得切架..."},{"pid":"1aa10f4766e31f07487e6e97971585eceb9c6fd7","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8d2e697cf12b47d6a9b225e538ea80a11fe0680","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"463ed04f39bf913e396bf28c7862a2fb90bef047","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d9df54e3d60668197c648b3f63227c6fce0e8a","tid":1406163,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"觀察到新戰術：四散游擊，街坊落場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1402338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1402338</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"999936249c3131efb3c4be661f24669ce0d9c895","tid":1406163,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:29:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗打 對政府冇影響 <br />\n對真係揸權嘅土共更加冇影響<br />\n要一針見血 就要搵政權最著緊嘅野同佢玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"730648283e3ca4131fefbdac9a0114564ea44a7f","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9de4d1951294ae1ee94d800bb3fa869c98612e6","tid":1406163,"uid":164517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"買左麵包"},{"pid":"028b45fc4b7ced94f61ecb79cca481320b606992","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:31:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9feb880f2fcb58857bbd6946c9f14b9d95a5a38","tid":1406163,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67eb3d0f80516830252cdef31e7d291819c3dde5","tid":1406163,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:32:19.000Z","msg":"觀塘、九龍灣、鰂魚涌<br />\n<br />\n三大被嚴重低估對香港既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁多Big4、銀行Back,Mid office。呢啲地方死左對銀行好大打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />數又過唔到、錢又禁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要搞搞中環好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> back office班狗唔洗理"},{"pid":"1db7e5ebd140fb35d53adb29d574840e770fa65f","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"38ac767e07bcc609b26189847faff517bce417fb","tid":1406163,"uid":267235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:33:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該入一入黎幫手推post</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【8.5三罷】如果朝早所有人遊車河!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404800</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cc3YftZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCc3YftZ.png&h=73d6d6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUfS7Za.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUfS7Za.png&h=2961d9b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb74102f155f92777965addf92b7e72564d01233","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:35:57.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"009d24a0b5fc91bf27d086a77a15ec855256af16","tid":1406163,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{